          <msContents>
            <summary>Manuscript used for consultation or teaching is an arrangement of and commentary on the sūtras of the grammarian Pāṇini. It is part of the Siddhāntakaumudī. There is a super-commentary by Nāgeśabhaṭṭa, the Laghuśabdenduśekhara, running parallel above and below the root text.</summary>
